%% Notifications — event-driven + scheduled messaging (SMS-first for PH, email where natural)
%% This is shared infra invoked by other workflows; it does not own business logic, only delivery.
%% Channels: SMS via Semaphore (PH local aggregator, primary), Email (verification, staff invites, optional copies).
%% Keep SMS single-segment GSM-7 (≤160 chars, no emoji/accents) to avoid multi-segment billing.
flowchart TD
    %% --- Two ways a notification originates ---
    subgraph Triggers
        EvtOTP[Public booking: OTP requested]
        EvtVerify[Signup: email verification]
        EvtInvite[Staff invite created]
        EvtConfirm[Booking confirmed / rescheduled / cancelled]
        EvtRequest[Booking request received → business]
        EvtDecision[Request approved / declined → customer]
        Sched[Scheduler tick]
    end

    %% --- Scheduled reminders resolve to concrete events ---
    Sched --> ScanDue[Scan upcoming appointments]
    ScanDue --> LeadTime{Booked ≥ 5h ahead?}
    LeadTime -->|No, < 5h lead| NoReminder[Skip — too close to send] --> End([Done])
    LeadTime -->|Yes| DueNow{Reminder due?<br/>5h before start}
    DueNow -->|No, not yet| End
    DueNow -->|Yes| EvtReminder[Appointment reminder]

    %% --- All events funnel into the dispatcher ---
    EvtOTP --> Build
    EvtVerify --> Build
    EvtInvite --> Build
    EvtConfirm --> Build
    EvtRequest --> Build
    EvtDecision --> Build
    EvtReminder --> Build

    Build[Build message:<br/>template + recipient + channel + locale] --> Audience{Recipient audience?}

    %% Business-facing alerts never use SMS (cost control) — in-app + email only
    Audience -->|Business: new request,<br/>staff alerts| BizDeliver[/Deliver in-app + email<br/>never SMS/] --> Logged

    %% Customer/user-facing messages choose a channel by type
    Audience -->|Customer / user| Channel{Channel for this type?}
    Channel -->|Transactional auth<br/>OTP, reminder, booking updates| SMS[Resolve SMS recipient]
    Channel -->|Email-native<br/>email verification, staff invite| Email[Resolve email recipient]

    %% --- Always-send: OTP, email verification, cancellations. Opt-out: reminders + booking confirmations ---
    SMS --> Essential{Essential message?<br/>OTP, email verification, cancellation}
    Essential -->|No — reminder / booking confirmation| OptOut{Recipient opted out?}
    OptOut -->|Yes| Skip[Skip + log suppressed] --> End
    OptOut -->|No| SendSMS
    Essential -->|Yes| SendSMS[/Send via Semaphore SMS/]
    Email --> SendEmail[/Send via email provider/]

    %% --- Delivery handling ---
    SendSMS --> SMSResult{Delivered?}
    SMSResult -->|Yes| Logged[(Log delivery + status)]
    SMSResult -->|No| Retry{Retries left?}
    Retry -->|Yes| SendSMS
    Retry -->|No| Fallback{Email on file?}
    Fallback -->|Yes| SendEmail
    Fallback -->|No| FailLog[(Log failure + flag for follow-up)] --> End

    SendEmail --> EmailResult{Delivered?}
    EmailResult -->|Yes| Logged
    EmailResult -->|No| EmailRetry{Retries left?}
    EmailRetry -->|Yes| SendEmail
    EmailRetry -->|No| FailLog

    Logged --> End
